You can see the same information for free with other apps or a browser. AIS only works near the coast, and if the port in question has implemented the AIS system, several important ports in South America do not have AIS,  such as Manaus Brazil, or La Guaira Venezuela. To see ships in the middle of the Atlantic needs to be done with satellites, and those are expensive subscription services.
